description: The video shows a digital image of a blonde woman with curly, retro-style hair. She bats her eyes at us as if flirting. There is a coy smile on her face with bright red lipstick. Her skin is light and she has a blush on her cheeks. She's wearing a green top and has her hands posed under her chin as if she's daydreaming. Around her are sparkling, four-pointed stars that appear and disappear.
